#### 📈 Plots

 1. Use the pandas `plot` method to graphically represent the contents of the dataframe.

 2. Repeat the operation, representing only the values of `S`, `I`, and `R`.

 3. Repeat the operation, representing only the values of `S`, `I`, and `R` and using the `plot.area` method with the `stacked=True` option.

 4. Go back to step 2, adding `T` to the selected variables.

 5. Represent the same variables with the same method, but only for the first year of the epidemic.

![](images/SIR-pandas-5.svg)

