```python
>>> df_SIR.plot.area(stacked=True)
<AxesSubplot:xlabel='date'>
>>> plt.ylim((0.0, 100.0))
(0.0, 100.0)
>>> plt.show()
```

![](images/SIR-pandas-3.svg)


```python
>>> df_SIRT = df[["S", "I", "R", "T"]]
>>> df_SIRT.plot()
>>> plt.show()
```

